==English==

===Etymology===
[[spam]] + [[advertizement]] (intentional misspelling of [[advertisement]])

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{internet}} A type of unsolicited e-mail ([[spam]]) that specifically [[advertise]]s a product.

Also; any advertisement which covers a broad spectrum of media in a non-targeted blanket campaign where one feels that there is no escaping it.  Typically so poorly done as to be remembered for the annoyance than the product itself.